text: Catelynn Lowell is pregnant! The Teen Mom OG star is expecting her third child with her husband, Tyler Baltierra, Us Weekly can exclusively confirm. “ The big news is that we are expecting our rainbow baby. This baby is our rainbow after the storm. I ’ m super excited, ” Lowell, who teased an upcoming announcement on Instagram in August, tells Us Weekly exclusively. “ It was a huge shock at first. We were not planning it, especially after the miscarriage and how I went downhill with my mental illness. ” She added : “ We were going to wait a really long time.
